name: Jibaro
additionalNotes: Full-bodied blend featuring an Ecuadorian binder and wrapper surrounding Dominican ligero filler. Jibaros feature a delicate double figurado shape (pointed at both ends) rolled in the traditional Cuban entubado-style to facilitate the placement of ligero and other filler leaves in a finished cigar to deliver proper burn from beginning to end. Canimao Jibaros measure 5 5/8 x 50.
